      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single load configuration per ASTM F1717 standard protocol (compression-bending, 10 mm/min crosshead speed, ambient conditions). Only one UHMWPE block density (grade) employed. Test conditions factor achieves Gradation 2 only; this is the single factor below the required level of 3. Risk accepted given direct experimental corroboration of primary QoIs.",
